        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. BACKSTAGE AT CONCERT - NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="c4cbd59d-9897-401f-a8ea-be419378b54c">
      <Text>ZLATKO, ANDREJ, ANTE, and ANTE are sitting at a table backstage. They are snorting cocaine, drinking alcohol, and smoking cigarettes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="9ba20e4e-aa2b-450d-87a0-6b1818beee37">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="5d64f861-2477-49ab-b933-f4ff1281c518">
      <Text>Is this what you confiscated, huh?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="44f5d56e-ea73-4d78-89ca-fc1d2e55d73f">
      <Text>ZLATKO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="fc76ea50-3341-412b-8c70-35de88e62bd5">
      <Text>Part of it.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="2371ec9d-ee5e-4ac8-b5a0-d6d834411633">
      <Text>ZLATKO takes a brick of cocaine out of a bag and gives it to ANDREJ. ANDREJ takes the brick and puts it on the table.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="dc3c6482-56bb-48fb-a349-671578863e9d">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="61068e3a-812b-489b-9b59-6a4297a19587">
      <Text>And the weed?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="2bbdc874-ce83-410c-a603-2cf0e759fbd9">
      <Text>ANTE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="d7d0f1b0-3841-4543-906b-19fafd0e0794">
      <Text>We have something. A kilo and a half.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="1357b068-4829-4a29-b798-6504fe0d4d8f">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="44223de5-c2fa-4bf3-85dc-e25882a1a462">
      <Text>What goes up, must come down.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="eb68f48b-14c8-4f9d-b75e-8fcb7e9e9d62">
      <Text>ANDREJ stabs his knife into a kilo of cocaine, and sniffs some of the coke off of the knife.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="acaebead-c314-4f2e-b99a-3c10da06efc6">
      <Text>ZLATKO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="50e42d20-6623-4bec-8729-9859eb5663c2">
      <Text>Have you seen the waitress, isn't she hot?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="78adae75-83ff-4123-93a4-fa41db1d9c05">
      <Text>ANTE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="681fcd05-b966-4fce-aaaf-78210b624991">
      <Text>Yes, she has a piercing on her left nipple. That's in fashion now.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7d46c954-996b-43b2-84b7-f878af208c9d">
      <Text>ZLATKO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="d4c2c87c-0f5b-4476-90ce-bbe901c0bac3">
      <Text>Have you been with her?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="2dac2805-60bf-4311-a4ae-b8ff827914a8">
      <Text>ANTE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="9a5d527a-63d3-4e96-a726-4eb961dce0db">
      <Text>Yes, she's not bad. But violent. She slapped me, and I hit her, she started throwing her heels at me. Crazy bitch, she almost hit my eye.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c37f6da1-608f-48f4-a3d3-1925c27fdd8d">
      <Text>ZLATKO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="bc3aaedd-6328-4f52-a038-32c3b11fa6e8">
      <Text>And why did she slap you?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="843c285c-2741-4f73-a6e7-24bf833ca82b">
      <Text>ANTE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="df2a1057-afd6-4af8-b12f-4c71a92e7622">
      <Text>Because she's retarded.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="d5299542-7a53-4692-b738-7b2d8acee4da">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="990057a1-424f-4ce6-81f2-3791c3054160">
      <Text>Luce is coming later. For you Zlatko, as we agreed.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="f723ed84-13da-4f7a-b09a-854e07eea319">
      <Text>ZLATKO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="5fa40d4e-903e-40a8-80a1-c50217800cdd">
      <Text>Thank you, boss.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="138fc3e8-b5a6-49e9-ba60-df444e2fdb11">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="0d3de37d-e953-486a-9322-4b0d7dc52151">
      <Text>Anything for you, dear.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="b0cee867-09c7-480f-8a2e-7495a8766702">
      <Text>VUJO, DUJE and PERE approach ANDREJ.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="4b66fc82-345c-43aa-809d-94918b12d77f">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="095afe8e-45fa-4f25-a35a-d1c872c97494">
      <Text>Hi czar.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="69c67807-ec6d-493f-988a-c90f9b448f08">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="1f14e30e-a2ee-4ad3-880c-67d6a3a548cd">
      <Text>Where you been my worm?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="4652c92f-80a8-4bf0-b6d2-0a257ff037fa">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="abf9a238-3e28-4480-82de-2915b19bce26">
      <Text>This is Dujan and Pere.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="e835a595-e686-4109-801c-8d33589d4d5d">
      <Text>ANDREJ gives DUJE his hand. They shake hands.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="5b68c802-150f-448c-a697-d980f5f1d536">
      <Text>ANDREJ smiles as he looks at DUJE.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="36ba8f55-265f-41b6-890e-b66aa02c7e1c">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="2cf5563b-e8b1-4dd1-a741-758edb4b7d93">
      <Text>Whose are you?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="628031d0-7fed-41c3-beb9-9350ca81f0fc">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="555b8d64-7185-47b1-bd98-f17bcf8e0b5f">
      <Text>Luce's brother. She hangs around here.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="84f3f95e-6846-4192-b777-79525708c4c7">
      <Text>ANDREJ and PERE shake hands.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c21bc4d8-1160-4805-88fc-c3203ae40110">
      <Text>ANDREJ (TO DUJE)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="f20312c7-1213-4a60-a2c8-b2461a11c4bf">
      <Text>Oh, Luce, I've seen her, yeah.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="f52ff4d2-e2be-4c0b-b8bf-77e05553c569">
      <Text>ANDREJ shows 4 lines of cocaine on the table with the movement of his hand.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="63423ffb-cd0f-4be7-befb-f6ea49c444ff">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="f831eada-2f74-46e5-b6bb-d9ff3afbf842">
      <Text>Serve yourselves.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="07c21084-4661-4a5b-bc7d-3d74906c0c23">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="3b9b598d-2ed4-4b03-9b91-d7cc4226729b">
      <Text>Is it coke?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="92d19c28-d469-4292-8a89-8c70e383505e">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="b0edd6ae-9f38-42f4-b721-7340cfbeabde">
      <Text>Yes, and not bad coke while we're at it.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="210341e7-a300-4c61-99b2-d437f64317c0">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="65779af8-09b0-4ad4-bc3a-d6e80bdea41f">
      <Text>He doesn't like speed.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="0f403b58-34f7-4c66-8499-25f24c523326">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="51229139-34c9-456a-88c3-52ca6e9d4d49">
      <Text>Boy has standards.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="0781cec7-9062-4411-81b7-6198934dc9ff">
      <Text>VUJO sniffs one line, then PERE.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="de107535-f701-4c55-9650-1a194c87acac">
      <Text>DUJE </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> ANDREJ </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sniff</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">their</Text>
      <Text> line at </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> same time, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">their</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">cheeks</Text>
      <Text> touch.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="be488e05-5a51-45b1-b57c-ecb028b6bc84">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="27" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="95cc3803-5704-4030-b496-e715f6eb331a">
      <SceneProperties Length="2 1/8" Page="27" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="LUCE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MANIRA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PALMINA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">INT</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CONCERT</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="36b3f550-804f-4e33-9f4f-c6bd975e2dda">
      <Text>PALMINA, MANIRA, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> LUCE are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">standing</Text>
      <Text> at a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">high</Text>
      <Text> table on </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">their</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">feet</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="ae93cf30-fef4-451f-8390-4e9965e6187f">
      <Text>All </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">three</Text>
      <Text> are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">drinking</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">gin</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">tonic</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="ef73da5b-e0da-4a29-b5c6-9721fd5be7fb">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="ccc670da-9fac-49fb-8823-93c663f34300">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">What</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">kind</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">of</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">clientele</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">been</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">having</Text>
      <Text>?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="6165e42f-2afd-4b1a-ac30-126be3469bed">
      <Text>LUCE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="bf862963-6b33-472e-9110-9128491dc9cf">
      <Text>Ah. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">I'm</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">booked</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">by</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Renata's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">father</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">in</Text>
      <Text> half </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">an</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">hour</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c39b2e03-638f-4f66-a320-6ae0e7c9f6a4">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="8be77e42-4e2a-46c2-805f-4d2035c5eedb">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">What</Text>
      <Text>?! </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">The</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">cop</Text>
      <Text>?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c881a6c1-3eac-43d7-89ba-53a4e4f8ee31">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="3beba8af-3d38-4c7c-a663-c557929b5946">
      <Text>Are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">serious</Text>
      <Text>?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="dae4a094-2271-47d3-96a7-5aca4251e55a">
      <Text>LUCE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="a2e16f38-c8ff-41f7-876d-e70457f870e3">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Yeah</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">he's</Text>
      <Text> a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">regular</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7abf541e-172a-4e0e-acec-fcccd9e56fd6">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="32ead1b9-4720-453a-b9e7-02bf89100ffe">
      <Text>Ah, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">weird</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="004043ba-8fa7-4dcc-ac13-31f1962bf065">
      <Text>Pause.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="3a88d6ff-913f-4472-b58c-641101099a7f">
      <Text>LUCE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="25c56184-684f-4d0e-bf3d-cc92452cd60c">
      <Text>So when are you two leaving?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e3fc28cf-6822-42f4-b305-a3b6d20de018">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="69c04d3c-eed2-40b0-8d87-280ab22957d1">
      <Text>In 2 weeks.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="3cc8dd03-7f13-4777-b432-9a7ec6bcc6ed">
      <Text>PALMINA (TO LUCE)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="eecb2c81-5b14-409a-85b7-325b44872b30">
      <Text>Come with us.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="4022e13f-c441-4d2f-a6bf-b05260ac24d9">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="fc2b27e4-cf74-4432-b341-cb27fd11db61">
      <Text>Exactly. Be a lady, a waitress, a bartender.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="b4b2a758-b5a8-4482-8f44-6b4b90c6c94e">
      <Text>LUCE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="5d3dad3b-a10f-46ba-90de-ef061f323d44">
      <Text>I work as a waitress down at Šteta.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="6a6b6307-ea6c-40c7-8c0e-053d681f9e1f">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="3dfc314c-9831-4941-84b5-3f83dac04663">
      <Text>Booked and busy.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c0ab606c-ad3e-4a1d-84c5-a760914bd65e">
      <Text>LUCE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="a2317b84-b7b8-4f01-a75d-cf52dcf2ea38">
      <Text>But I'm an international woman. It wouldn't be bad to be a dominatrix. I can't do that here, but I could do it there, and the money is good.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a96bcef6-64a0-4938-9159-73fa3c4b614e">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="8bcd6557-45e1-45e1-bd3d-43ff8c857bd6">
      <Text>Well, we should. Three of us together. High-heeled boots and stomping on pathethic men's balls for money. Come with us, baby!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e59c8060-337e-40f2-a0bf-c01e21ecbc07">
      <Text>LUCE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="b721ff84-cd97-49ff-bce1-8fcd20b0eb8c">
      <Text>Yeah. Smoking cigarretes and blowing smoke in their faces while they're suffocating.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="732d69ca-e3a3-4890-8dbb-b120b874590b">
      <Text>All three laugh.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="55432eb1-692a-4243-b9ca-3d776664aa68">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="98ddf58d-ec67-41d7-9728-07e6b33f6ea5">
      <Text>Luce, seriously, come.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="e3d80ec9-911f-4ecd-8ff6-76079df32824">
      <Text>PALMINA and LUCE look at each other.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a21df897-bb79-417e-9eca-07d9a8294e45">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="31241a1c-a85a-4310-ae18-673165c676fe">
      <Text>There are more eccentric people there.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="ec476b24-a8d5-4320-99f9-386d8f714d1b">
      <Text>LUCE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="4684bdff-e5dd-4c15-9c3b-c4e5e2a6b3cc">
      <Text>I believe that, yeah.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a0874edb-0fb4-4d6a-85e7-18a0155c3b3d">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="3eb8e3c7-a863-40a5-b18d-74bd8f198293">
      <Text>You're coming. I can see it in your eyes that you're coming.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="111d4026-bcab-44a6-beb2-044e749934de">
      <Text>MANIRA laughs.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="b12fcf30-af4a-4457-b75f-cdc76527290c">
      <Text>LUCE laughs.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="3fae85b0-9e40-49c1-915d-75e6a4359f53">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="dea0e51c-9c83-47c3-a34d-c69fcbf7b1fb">
      <Text>PALMINA, MANIRA and LUCE toast with 3 shots of tequila.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="529acb9d-277d-44e9-8674-5eb38ba56a6a">
      <Text>PALMINA sucks on a lemon.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="4ef76fbd-53e1-4f55-8927-60ca8b2bade7">
      <Text>All 3 laugh and look at MAGDALENA on stage.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="6e525fa3-1811-4fc9-8893-9b504110d87b">
      <Text>PALMINA eats a lemon peel.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="4a343d74-8fa2-4cd5-82a5-07dddb50e247">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="ff2d059e-841d-4f5b-bc1c-12d086084165">
      <Text>What a specimen, everything is see-through.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="70c4a206-6956-4dd4-8819-bf55fb89a9fd">
      <Text>LUCE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="ed71ebdd-21d8-4fa5-baf4-f4d5dfff19a7">
      <Text>And then I'm a whore?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="cc978d25-662e-4128-b3da-02d88868fabb">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="19011b15-14d1-40a7-8485-d06f2c523a6e">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">You're</Text>
      <Text> a lady </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">compared</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">her</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="bb0b901d-d2e8-4cbf-bf74-a3cd30eeaeaf">
      <Text>All 3 </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">laugh</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="21bfbd91-ee30-4bb7-972b-55da4016ac06">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> LUCE </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">look</Text>
      <Text> at </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">each</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">other</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="115db2cd-05ae-49c2-8562-dcce162390db">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="28" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="d6b4d10e-0f5e-4d9e-b4ed-0a71a77e5cf8">
      <SceneProperties Length="1/8" Page="29" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">INT</Text>
      <Text>. IN </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">THE</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">TOILET</Text>
      <Text> AT </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">THE</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CONCERT</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="9cebbdff-35c9-431b-98df-931ddbe6ee0c">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> LUCE are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">making</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">out</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="aaffcebf-95c8-465f-b73b-2ec56be4cb89">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="29" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="4607f372-aa65-4d52-a256-fd29f3d37f96">
      <SceneProperties Length="5 7/8" Page="29" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="ANDREJ">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="ANTE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="ZLATKO">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">INT</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">BACKSTAGE</Text>
      <Text> AT </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">THE</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CONCERT</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="ab3bb93c-284a-42cb-a0ef-582ceaeb14e9">
      <Text>ANDREJ </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> ZLATKO smoke </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">cigarettes</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="700de94c-dc32-4a08-9165-60dda0e555e6">
      <Text>ZLATKO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="c27bc44c-611c-4bba-b2a0-ee7ac2ad6af3">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">The</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Netherlands</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">that's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">nothing</Text>
      <Text>, Rotterdam </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">has</Text>
      <Text> a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">closed</Text>
      <Text> port. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Now</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">they're</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">going</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">through</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Antwerp</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Belgium</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Because</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">what's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">an</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">open</Text>
      <Text> port. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">And</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Dutch</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">aren't</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">quick</Text>
      <Text> to take </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">bribes</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">they're</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">strange</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">people</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">they</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">like</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">rules</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">And</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">these</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Belgians</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">that's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">different</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">they're</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">closer</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">French</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">rats</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">they'll</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">fuck</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">over</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">And</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">who's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">collecting</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">all</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">that</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">money</Text>
      <Text>? </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Moroccans</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">filthy</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">animals</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Everything's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">going</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">through</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">them</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="1aa15a5c-4a9d-4e6a-b2de-188d5714cf5d">
      <Text>ANTE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="7e47cbbb-8b42-47ee-9fcf-99c64e86e78a">
      <Text>When I was working in Spain, at 2 in the morning I was walking towards my apartment, when a Moroccan beat up a homeless man and stole his small suitcase. I couldn't believe it. It's all that man has, and you take it away from him. Well, that's not the way.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="adbacdf1-9801-4637-9128-d3682df86edd">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="b7c11fcd-8966-4f47-a799-96ac5240137e">
      <Text>Every nation has it's filthy animals.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="1b584415-00b5-43e8-9797-7d1eb679fc52">
      <Text>ZLATKO makes two lines of cocaine with a card.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="d85f937e-3a01-48f3-8042-588f4cf21676">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="f7309e5e-97e3-41b1-b935-c114fd20f853">
      <Text>Zlatko, how was Luce last time? Was she good?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="7d52aad0-7a8a-411f-ae3f-e045b955403a">
      <Text>ZLATKO snorts one line of cocaine, then another, with the rolled-up 20 euro bill.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e89e2be4-1172-4f35-996c-a5a5582989ca">
      <Text>ZLATKO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="940d254d-a78d-42d0-b864-cbeb4b128072">
      <Text>Amazing. Luce is not just a whore. Luce is the woman I love.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a263c295-7aa0-46ed-9a50-f72dda41c61b">
      <Text>ANTE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="6f03382f-8700-47f3-941a-7f40adaf3fa6">
      <Text>How can you live two lives?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="81fe0875-c256-4e3c-8344-0294c4195953">
      <Text>ZLATKO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="a901a40e-d093-4090-b473-43c7405f1a92">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">When</Text>
      <Text> I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">was</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">divorcing</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">my</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">first</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">wife</Text>
      <Text>, Tihana, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">we</Text>
      <Text> had to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">decide</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">who</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">would</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">get</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">building</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">which</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">was</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">hers</Text>
      <Text> on </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">papers</Text>
      <Text>, but I had </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">paid</Text>
      <Text> for </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">it</Text>
      <Text>. We </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">didn't</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">want</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">go</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">court</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">we</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">talked</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">like</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">two</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">people</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">we</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">agreed</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">that</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">she</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">would</Text>
      <Text> put </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">building</Text>
      <Text> on </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">my</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">name</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">that</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">she</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">would</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">get</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">house</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">And</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">my</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">accountant</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">calls</Text>
      <Text> me, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">says</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">that</Text>
      <Text> Tihana put </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">building</Text>
      <Text> on </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">her</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sister's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">name</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">She</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">took</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">everything</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">from</Text>
      <Text> me. But no </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">matter</Text>
      <Text> how </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">many</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">times</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">she</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">betrayed</Text>
      <Text> me, I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">can</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">never</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">get</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">used</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">that</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">feeling</Text>
      <Text>. Do </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">know</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">what</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">she</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">left</Text>
      <Text> me? A </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">parrot</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">When</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">I'm</Text>
      <Text> at home, I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">have</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">listen</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">first</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">my</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">wife</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">then</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">parrot</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">it</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">repeats</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">everything</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="1c987ec3-6b11-464f-a04f-e6504dcbd511">
      <Text>ZLATKO (AS </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">HIS</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">WIFE</Text>
      <Text>)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="dfe7ef93-f58b-4095-980d-d8764dc3b6e2">
      <Text>"You </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">asshole</Text>
      <Text>!"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="2f273bc8-f15b-411c-9eff-f019694b547a">
      <Text>ZLATKO (AS A </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">PARROT</Text>
      <Text>)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="adb852e0-5c57-42a8-a45c-a9d2bfa745ee">
      <Text>"You </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Asshole</Text>
      <Text>!"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="f1016657-9b9e-4ba7-8ef6-e5dca5d53524">
      <Text>ANDREJ </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> ANTE </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">laugh</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="89a2b135-0c01-4751-9004-7cae86446caf">
      <Text>ZLATKO (AS </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">HIS</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">WIFE</Text>
      <Text>)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="35de3495-a2c3-4c51-ab2a-9587b47ac941">
      <Text>"</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Every</Text>
      <Text> time </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">it</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">rains</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">it's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">leaking</Text>
      <Text>!"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="03d08137-778c-4101-91c9-24e48f0cce6d">
      <Text>ZLATKO (AS A </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">PARROT</Text>
      <Text>)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="40dcaa83-67a7-4c8b-af3e-b4e4be0bd866">
      <Text>"</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">It's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">leaking</Text>
      <Text>!"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="f25c076e-e239-4505-9894-a43fb6285d0f">
      <Text>ANDREJ </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> ANTE </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">laugh</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="eae39ff6-908d-412e-8ea0-e52e05d20441">
      <Text>ZLATKO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="93f71653-d289-4ba5-b8c2-738ad72bb151">
      <Text>Where is it leaking?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="4b10c578-6004-404e-b523-d6383c844a25">
      <Text>ANTE laughs.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="0fe7bef6-c50b-466c-98f5-57a4a377c99c">
      <Text>ZLATKO (AS HIS WIFE)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="9d045cda-8719-4581-880e-ae8ae688dae5">
      <Text>"We have a black hole on the ceiling in the kitchen!"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="484a4e43-2dd8-4d04-8d0f-f941c65c96fd">
      <Text>ZLATKO (AS A PARROT)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="777defc7-6d22-4078-96b5-209c57eef643">
      <Text>"A black hole on the ceiling!"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="11a7a93b-9ad5-46af-9957-c945bf1b7233">
      <Text>ZLATKO (AS HIS WIFE)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="56ee285c-f6e1-4d7b-b7d8-8782a7c3d5d7">
      <Text>"You're never home before 2 am!"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="2ea68d88-443e-48b1-b8c3-dc476164cf94">
