    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="97868fad-baa0-4cce-9ea5-c803ff1b7c4e">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="ddc7f913-c25e-4877-b157-b03af2cfe25d">
      <Text>Erste!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="1653cb5e-385e-4f4e-8dd0-6fe15d8dac92">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="f515439a-d262-457c-8e9e-bd710e64a4c5">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Where've</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">been</Text>
      <Text> Paloma? </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">You're</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">not</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">around</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e3cfa3cc-a667-44bb-98e6-8e017f77d033">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="1bafcc80-893d-41c5-a6e5-ad1eee23b074">
      <Text>I was packing.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="d480b27b-1617-40c7-844f-002a754c5d2d">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="c28d71a8-1332-41b6-a3d0-3bdc0a782592">
      <Text>Where are you going?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="bff2ac2f-cc44-48ae-ad9a-cfa623be86cd">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="8b5797e4-ba07-4593-b325-a63f4dc745b2">
      <Text>I'm moving to Vienna.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="901610af-4e32-440e-a7cc-68200555b9a5">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="c2e4f605-6b2a-4fbb-8d28-28cf5767baf2">
      <Text>Aaa I see the kitty is back. So you are going together now.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="9c31be20-f389-46b3-a61d-329ea35951ae">
      <Text>ANDREJ (TO MANIRA)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="8f164281-e260-49c6-b21e-33e1810fb0d5">
      <Text>Where you at, kitty? Did you dominate the airport?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a3c76837-cade-45eb-a011-147740c01f75">
      <Text>MANIRA (TO THE DEALER)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="a5ee9f7f-cd0d-43e8-9744-17a850fd2902">
      <Text>Of course.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="565177b3-8509-451b-87d0-4a5dba51f05c">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="6f228096-94fa-4742-8cdd-886f39bb01c6">
      <Text>Some people are going to Vienna, and I'm doomed to our beautiful country. That's how my beans tuned out.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="5f7b5b7b-77fd-43a6-b888-9d9b21ad38ac">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="e011602c-d9e9-4f14-8b03-f20c2bf5bee0">
      <Text>Well, you can do this in Vienna too.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="9c4c08b3-ee0d-4314-9b05-0b5e98896874">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="188d2fc4-ac04-466c-a009-e01605e5d00d">
      <Text>Oh, yeah. And what are you going to do?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e5592065-c2df-49c6-a78a-8daa4afb6c03">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="b884e45a-ad6c-4718-8afb-cf741dd16cc9">
      <Text>I'll be a waitress.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="ab16dbac-cc5e-481d-801a-60025ac5a72c">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="d254067b-3700-4a56-9bbf-a82cc02d15d2">
      <Text>Well, it's good. Maybe there'll be tips.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a3ab7841-8c75-40eb-9fa6-cd0fe5aa7d51">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="bfe6bbee-2a85-4313-a6ef-9bddff067cfe">
      <Text>What is being sold usually? Any coke?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="204776cb-92f9-437d-a5da-993c85aa00c5">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="c0699ba8-6f72-4cd6-99b1-1e83aaba2601">
      <Text>No coke, brother, just speed. People don't have money, bro.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="50f881af-6781-465b-8f85-4f66a54471c6">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="88c28170-d8b6-4043-bbe8-4f05db517408">
      <Text>Where did you get the money from then?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="0f4be203-16ea-4e86-9f9e-a504635dea55">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="c0b50c22-e496-463d-a954-0918f837c68c">
      <Text>For ten years they've been asking me where I get my money, and I'm working.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c4b41bf2-9d08-4473-953c-c1594c583fbc">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="111ced31-136c-4656-b6ca-3d725280d603">
      <Text>Oh yeah.. And where's Anđela?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c306bd61-b182-40b4-90de-8f2529279d01">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="2df0377f-f957-4aba-b434-008d0cfc56fc">
      <Text>Anđelaaa. Do you know that because of her I stopped snorting on Tuesdays. Monday is hard, I can't get rid of it, Wednesday is students day, Thursday is a little Friday, Friday is Friday, Saturday is the weekend, Sunday is after. So I can only get rid of Tuesday. But only for her.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="bfc652e2-f4f8-47d1-a815-ecc1ddcf80e8">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="5ee0d2e8-446c-4d5c-a00d-be928d3f14c7">
      <Text>So it's love.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="525d250c-c914-4263-b436-aeb6e58e95d9">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="b13c3911-0cb4-4499-9780-2cbc5faa3b82">
      <Text>Huge. And why you want the trip? Are witches preparing a sexual assassination?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="947bfacb-af8d-487e-ad4a-87cc0d634ece">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="b85dd11b-2b3d-4d2a-872c-4adc678b82b1">
      <Text>That's right. Under the stars.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c84095f1-a27a-403a-96c4-1478c748470d">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="42e879b5-8b5a-4cc9-bff2-5b9f979eef3a">
      <Text>Listen, I made pancakes the other day, melted the weed into the butter, and my dog ate 2.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="d019c84c-932f-4686-9a64-c89b534c2a19">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="ef9ef8f8-fb6c-464f-9275-276fcd4d1a1b">
      <Text>Is he even allowed to eat that?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="3ec077ef-eed3-4b9d-97a4-5ede45664cd9">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="0c75af90-181f-4a6e-96d7-b021cd81e42a">
      <Text>Why wouldn't he be allowed? He's a collateral smoker anyway.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="8d723765-23ae-45f6-94b7-fed6ec45a16e">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="20c84f30-2148-47bd-9046-3806fed7b43e">
      <Text>Yeah.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="596b061a-44fa-4283-b296-c6ac550c71e9">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="d38dde7f-10d8-4d5d-8dd6-30bc610ce315">
      <Text>Nothing.. Here's 2 for 20.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="18a0f86a-be02-41c4-ac70-8b854ee52479">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="c38d35c7-f2da-463d-909e-fdb9b786b685">
      <Text>That's expensive. I need to save up for Vienna.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="ae9328f7-4de8-45bb-87e5-60fed17113cb">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="09d463e3-23b0-4a62-9871-91dd783d9263">
      <Text>Everything is expensive here. It's cheaper in Vienna.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="51024d4c-bd6e-469d-8e9d-f0ba5f7be604">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="be116052-82b7-45de-8d6f-68c90c844cc9">
      <Text>And are these good?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="40cece2f-7117-4533-964a-0ee020e76cb5">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="685e780c-9ed3-4c10-8556-503740a0430d">
      <Text>Yes, but depends on your tolerance. Get 4, 2 for you, 2 for her.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c61bb30b-f3db-4391-bcef-f005b8cf9f1e">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="98a0015f-83e7-4526-88d6-ee761db2a8a4">
      <Text>It's not for us, it's for a friend, so I thought at least 2 for him. Can it be for 15?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="33193d52-c352-42ba-9259-9525d966e50b">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="01698d79-9b22-4952-b954-6f0e3e41abb8">
      <Text>Can't be.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c848d4c4-b474-4f8e-857f-35461e9b68b8">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="f54e0dfd-1170-4c8c-9e57-582626bbcbd2">
      <Text>And can it be 2 for 20 and a gram to smoke?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7494a9a5-e2fc-440c-8d4f-331773fc20af">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="6f51acb0-ac5a-4cfe-ab01-afe99ec7f148">
      <Text>Okay.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="73209e69-9141-428c-9d98-01cb1965fc7a">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="978fe43b-a78e-44a6-ad73-8aeef6b138a9">
      <Text>There you go. Thank You.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="40d118af-6108-426b-b080-a48e3ee2ded1">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="df2c07cd-ce2d-4688-8eba-95a219d7c8fb">
      <Text>Thank You Austria.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="97b9beb8-0be0-41ee-b2b6-4b71d8a4a578">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="89623c93-d2e2-4665-be42-213d757be928">
      <Text>Ciao.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7cf0145f-3b6b-4967-ba48-0d22c50a653d">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="d3ec2bba-9612-430b-b9b5-88f7ea51ca88">
      <Text>Auf Wiedersehen.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="49e9efc1-36c1-47b7-9b0a-b89827a2e42e">
      <Text>PALMINA gets back in the car.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="71b57572-caec-4c76-a07d-a96ceb58eb72">
      <Text>MATE is still playing the guitar, PALMINA starts the car and drives off.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="b1344115-8378-48f6-9969-3e37889c33f7">
      <Text>MATE starts singing along to the playing.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="b8ed4ebb-bce0-4e08-8030-d282e3bf0cc0">
      <Text>PALMINA turns the car on and starts driving.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="54effdad-ff7b-41a0-9af9-d845fc4b3592">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="37" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="8d064365-cbe8-4e9a-aec2-99235887e941">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 6/8" Page="44" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MANIRA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MATE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PALMINA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>EXT. IN FRONT OF THE PEACH TREE - EVENING</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="ed16008a-6a61-42bd-b1d5-3f1a73ec867a">
      <Text>PALMINA, MANIRA AND MATE are leaning against a parked car and eating peaches.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="ef334a97-5abb-4398-b9e1-9080838972fb">
      <Text>MATE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="4a3914b5-a7c4-4c81-8560-cd8957214716">
      <Text>Let's eat and look at each other.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="fbf6e2d6-856e-4bc0-85d0-344a50cd1faa">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="7c561a29-4502-4ea6-8a2c-b22c150054ea">
      <Text>Let's.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="401f49bb-d23c-46f1-9269-71b4755dac1c">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="e7f6781c-5903-454e-ace7-613dd4f823f5">
      <Text>Palmina also says that sometimes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="3ddbf535-8562-4e26-bfca-4ff915f54613">
      <Text>MATE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="9f7753c8-b541-483e-a20e-41c227b1325b">
      <Text>And why do you keep a guitar in the trunk?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="fb045638-481a-4038-b4aa-8c59b9bb6181">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="9da1e910-9070-42dd-84ad-96c3bad1b984">
      <Text>You never know.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="7d61d354-1f99-443e-9bbd-b13a91255d6a">
      <Text>MANIRA eats the peach first. She throws the stone on the floor to the side.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="0a448fb1-c5f4-424f-8d58-d15b0effb7a7">
      <Text>MANIRA rolls a cigarette.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="fdb566d6-cfb8-4a0d-8809-7ac739537fae">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="97b87ecd-f980-4760-909f-01f952b1f31c">
      <Text>That's more important than a spare tire. I know how to play the guitar, but I don't know how to change a tire.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="51dfb311-eca5-4092-a08f-27648e1da44b">
      <Text>MATE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="7d6cebae-10e0-4fc5-aae4-51d272202704">
      <Text>To be honest, I don't know either. I'm feminized.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="1396a52b-fd8f-48f1-a8b1-bfc6c0b01c10">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="82da1125-8461-45ad-8b64-46919bb00244">
      <Text>I see.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="593b6795-1f26-4021-9582-b92259082921">
      <Text>MANIRA looks in her pockets for a lighter, but can't find one.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="6a317d63-7fdd-49f8-8f95-f8ccdd56316c">
      <Text>MANIRA gets in the car and looks for a lighter.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="28075c21-6074-4a9a-8a14-9c3fe2a8c918">
      <Text>MATE (TO PALMINA)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="f0d3629f-f5e9-458c-bece-41997d8645b1">
      <Text>Am I a good-looking guy to you?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e81372a5-f197-4a63-8720-9ffabf36b68f">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="41fd9cda-ba53-41ed-81f0-5f3f8d8a6d0d">
      <Text>I don't know. You're kind of soft. Gay.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="d11eb42c-311d-4ca9-8813-c7e240aaa9a0">
      <Text>MATE gets visibly insulted by this comment and starts getting defensive.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="97b26e55-ef4e-4097-b187-4e8b8acadfd5">
      <Text>MATE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="1281a3af-7e89-4eaa-a75c-ef3276dae46b">
      <Text>Wait. I'm not gay! What's wrong with you?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="9d88909e-56e0-46a0-a2c4-bd3dbb3ee652">
      <Text>MATE grabs PALMINA's ass.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="1adefd91-95ad-48fa-97bf-86e4f7742111">
      <Text>MANIRA sees what's happening and gets out of the car.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="fd5f0e58-3acd-4454-b296-155f78b5f047">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="5c95e461-b731-4ebf-9b77-2f36976a2928">
      <Text>Don't touch me, who are you?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="884ab671-70ba-4dcf-9b51-9354548037b2">
      <Text>MATE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="7f1caaa4-10fc-4b3e-998f-aefb8551eae4">
      <Text>Admit that you like me at least a little bit.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="565a3282-1fd5-4d7c-94fb-a242502e1a88">
      <Text>MATE grabs PALMINA's waist.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e96aef3f-fe10-4554-86c9-88e1758fdf93">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="c598ccf4-24c0-4396-a2cb-4c7058b93363">
      <Text>Get away from me!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="1198f589-1642-4819-af94-b8689d13b0fc">
      <Text>MANIRA appears behind MATE and hits him over the head with his guitar.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="21bc24af-07e9-47b1-a320-8b0bfab33487">
      <Text>MATE falls to the floor.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="348598a1-8307-4eac-8ace-7e90c9500294">
      <Text>PALMINA kicks MATE in the balls three times with her right foot.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="08e2f1cf-2cea-4cad-ac24-91bdd7f3271c">
      <Text>MATE cries as she lies on the floor.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="71144c2d-2218-410c-9f43-8a45f14819c7">
      <Text>PALMINA AND MANIRA both spit in MATE's face.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a076aca8-d507-4613-901c-39e6fea484da">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="8ad4ec5e-3946-4445-bf2b-a5ba38e85ea9">
      <Text>What a piece of shit.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="7e5b5218-8957-4f01-9538-7eb14d943d56">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="38" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="1038085e-610d-40e3-8f98-fbbd4bd2f96f">
      <SceneProperties Length="5/8" Page="46" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PERE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="VUJO">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. APARTMENT HALLAY - NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="f3f6805a-937e-4c8c-b5e6-37279fbc4c7d">
      <Text>PERE and VUJO talking.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c6867230-35e2-456b-925a-ba799d83c03d">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="3c8975ed-881a-4d6d-b403-8232398c01fa">
      <Text>He said 100 euros.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="6b94ab7b-fb7e-4eaa-9e49-1030978387fe">
      <Text>PERE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="3f528863-4086-4994-a676-2988129cdcd5">
      <Text>100 together, or 100 for you and 100 for me?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="d81850de-ab8c-43a7-9109-3d1ede2e7b06">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="3547610b-b3fb-4639-a1eb-2b545ea7a6c3">
      <Text>I don't know. Probably 100 each, come on bro, he's not a cheap asshole.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="157595fd-ebe0-4167-8d4b-dda1df8642e9">
      <Text>PERE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="e7b2c853-d567-45b2-9ebd-f9e09d1f790c">
      <Text>So why didn't you tell him that he should pay an advance? What if we come there and he doesn't give us anything?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="2a4f6126-5520-4510-801d-db12aa6be41b">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="9c8b321a-5268-46a4-af4d-d15b2e0586bb">
      <Text>Why are you stressing, come on..</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="2ad452bc-c455-4bd4-ad02-27e3ad392c6e">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="39" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="f7876353-9614-4ce3-9ca5-a9df1068ff8a">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="46" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DUJE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="VUJO">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. APARTMENT LIVING ROOM - NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="c69d50b7-b69c-4d7a-910d-a317b31bb236">
      <Text>VUJO walks towards DUJE who is sitting on the couch.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7b002350-a214-4f92-9719-3c64117f279a">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="79c5f427-1573-4704-adfb-ed9141a29628">
      <Text>Duje, I know a guy at whose place we can stay for free.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a3c523a4-28ff-42cb-ac8d-a30868c53724">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="2926900b-6ce9-4d3d-bd18-85050e6a42bd">
      <Text>Who?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="f94245c7-a63b-44cb-8ac1-52d99b102312">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="40" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="e7dec305-4158-40ef-8d9c-3c8d7175d723">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="47" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MIRO">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>EXT. IN FRONT OF A SMALL STORE - NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="75cdbd2e-47be-4174-baee-64a71858cfc7">
      <Text>MIRO, an old man, stops his car in front of the store, leaves it on, gets out of the car, and enters the store.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="13c2e9f7-efef-4d16-8980-24e2e96a2af7">
      <Text>A few moments later, DUJE, VUJO, and PERE run up to the car.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="686a3e25-1945-4477-82b2-fafc49babce3">
      <Text>VUJO gets in the front seat behind the wheel, DUJE gets in the passenger seat, and PERE gets in the back seat.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="5737521e-9638-4589-84d8-908896770791">
      <Text>VUJO puts the car in first gear and the car disappears from the frame in a second.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="0e3956e7-7190-48ca-8062-3291610b1ce3">
      <Text>MIRO leaves the store with a 0.5l glass bottle of beer in his hand, opens it with the keys, takes a sip, then looks in amazement where his car has disappeared to.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="8ca26aed-07cf-4b30-b9d4-01d4bd5cebb1">
      <Text>MIRO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="107b9c2f-cb52-456a-b12f-98f049df7f47">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Fucking</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">shit</Text>
      <Text>! </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Where</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">did</Text>
      <Text> I park </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">my</Text>
      <Text> car?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="5a5110e3-f1a7-46fb-95b8-8b02b2026954">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="41" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="9f4dc560-9391-4854-bb87-1d6b1c05a1d8">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="47" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">INT</Text>
      <Text>. IN </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">THE</Text>
      <Text> CAR - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="f3accd20-6ca6-48bc-a01e-06e532367b4f">
      <Text>Music </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">is</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">playing</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="1c6aa144-ee20-4582-ba4c-b3c6af1339d6">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">VUJO</Text>
      <Text>, DUJE, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> PERE are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">driving</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">in</Text>
      <Text> a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">stolen</Text>
      <Text> car.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="b07dd713-faaa-4027-b443-13850790b424">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="42" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="d8acf912-ec5c-4dd2-a085-a05544790fac">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 4/8" Page="47" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="ANDREJ">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PERE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="VUJO">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">INT</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">ANDREJ'S</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">LIVING</Text>
      <Text> ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="cbd39c1d-e99a-42f4-8ac1-ba40d4d90c7e">
      <Text>DUJE, PERE </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">VUJO</Text>
      <Text> are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sitting</Text>
      <Text> on </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">couch</Text>
      <Text>. ANDREJ </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">is</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sitting</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">in</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">an</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">armchair</Text>
      <Text>, a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">shotgun</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">is</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">above</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">him</Text>
      <Text> on </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">wall</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="02d979d0-e6b2-4543-bad9-003ffe4c3c67">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Everyone</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">is</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">drinking</Text>
