      <Text>Hmmmm. Mhmmmm. Aaaumm. Huummm. F-f-f-frrrrr. Fa-fa-fa-fa-fa-fa-fa...</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="61931a82-36f9-4902-bc8e-701fc083f108">
      <Text>Fa-fa-fa-fa-fa-fa. Aaaašššššsssss. Aha. I see you. An artist. You played the piano. You were left-handed, and now you're right-handed. You had a child. Want to guess if it's a boy or a girl?</Text>
