      <Text>A boy.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="45eb4fb2-59e9-4bbe-af0a-03715e057635">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="1eadf1f2-a569-42b7-be21-f34056aa4c5d">
      <Text>There you go. You had that kid with a prostitute, a model, that was your girlfriend. You paid for her tits. Then she told you she was trans. Your girlfriend was your boyfriend.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
