    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="e392b51a-010f-48e2-890e-7a8c9064d473">
      <Text>In Yugoslavia I couldn't buy a Coke, now I'm drinking a Coke and something else is missing. Freedom is when you're satisfied with what you have. When you don't ask for more. I admit that I ask for more.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
