    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="ecbcef73-b4df-40a7-8dad-402ffa5b8957">
      <Text>PALMINA and MANIRA are inside a tent. They have a light coming from inside, their shadows are visible.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
