      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="0401cc22-77cc-45b5-bdc3-7314b226de11">
      <Text>You'll learn quickly, you just need to know the basics to communicate. I once got a 200 euro tip from Germans, but they live in New York.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="9cf7c868-825a-4138-b271-619f2ea1fcb3">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="4c2e8eea-c349-4cdf-a9da-3a0d8bd7452d">
      <Text>Wow, that's nice.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="0400e4c2-c827-4f08-bf25-db2a08197984">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="4605f046-9c41-4ce7-8332-9205ab0a9b07">
      <Text>6 blond men, business meeting. They were sniffing in the toilet, because I don't know anyone who has to pee 5 times in half an hour. And the people I work with would always ask me if I had anything to sniff. No bro, I'm just a type A personality.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="17e8fdfa-5338-437e-9ab4-042afea29853">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="6be4449f-d8a9-4626-9230-fb9c490e9f4c">
      <Text>Fast and efficient.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="b978cdd7-a8e9-498d-9524-560e118fcc79">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="13298a57-5cca-4bad-b62c-08ed0a236c65">
      <Text>That day, my pride. When I'm here I don't have it. I just have FOMO. Nothing is happening.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="336761d3-adb8-480b-ba48-02d827646ddd">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="2a91c51a-17e1-4e0d-af4a-6b0aeded3adb">
      <Text>You're always complaining. You see how nice it is that it's not raining.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="fc49a79c-c04c-4052-8021-404399cf1bc3">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="f6e73119-6369-455d-b880-0ebbb5eb6532">
      <Text>Yeah.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="0d271df1-6f66-417c-bf77-f7c1c5b8bb15">
      <Text>Pause.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="ad31e0ea-6d57-46ca-b862-26f617a58345">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="7fab26a1-2bc2-4771-bfc1-0e0255e70566">
      <Text>What happened with Franco?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a17852cf-9324-43c9-b98d-d413ed0c4b3f">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="4cb0a151-5f0d-46a2-890b-935b854a927e">
      <Text>Loser.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="f923d685-2f33-4f67-8ca7-eef9e259e3b3">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="a93fd212-87c9-4e40-a518-137fc2f99916">
      <Text>He didn't prove himself?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
