      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="d07c1886-3d8c-47d3-b400-88ec70df3ca5">
      <Text>We are writing an exam, he starts beat boxing.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="68a88f17-17ec-434e-b8af-2c3cb440b65e">
      <Text>PALMINA laughs a lot.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="e6adea30-f18d-430c-9f91-81f53f142135">
      <Text>PALMINA beat boxing.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="026a371d-0763-4b22-b8f8-41e4d5dd3e71">
      <Text>MANIRA laughs a lot.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="53d5c470-2a38-4a68-a215-184438b01022">
      <Text>They both laugh out loud until slowly everything goes silent.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="10cddd9d-5037-45b1-8fa9-2eda0ff3a40c">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="48" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="92aa594c-a1d0-4ef2-bf17-bd1e8fbb9c90">
      <SceneProperties Length="7/8" Page="54" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="ANDREJ">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DUJE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. ANDREJ'S ROOM - NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="8e2f8751-d62a-40a0-adb3-2a491055c32c">
      <Text>DUJE slowly opens his eyes, and ANDREJ is standing and taking his clothes off.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="414225ed-5214-4597-be0d-f94f06184335">
      <Text>DUJE covers his head with a blanket.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="15cdc4d6-6deb-4cd5-8cd3-64bcb26d8b49">
      <Text>ANDREJ comes closer to DUJE and handcuffs DUJE'S left hand to the edge of the bed.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="e0cec617-4c93-49ec-ab37-e761a798da7c">
      <Text>ANDREJ sits on the edge of the bed next to DUJE.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="97c27298-9a3e-42d6-92dc-2ba27e155d92">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="3c3e5993-2433-45cb-a8de-5b4a234b2116">
      <Text>You're a hot cat. You have beautiful eyes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="d2d40941-170f-4563-97d5-60c9e83a64e6">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="6f406ddd-ef7b-402c-ad21-81577d381363">
      <Text>What is wrong with you?! What the fuck are you doing?!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e21279c8-92d9-4c51-a9e5-a2b9887a45ca">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="79b24ea1-446a-47c0-a502-c5dbcd7cdb5f">
      <Text>You don't like me? I would never hurt you. I will be gentle.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="bc79a038-17f0-4653-8525-8d184a55ff14">
      <Text>DUJE is trying to get out of handcuffs.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="b1403905-54fd-4769-a6c0-1ef3f2816d96">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="04ec0076-be73-4d9d-a2e8-4389d31a4133">
      <Text>I don't like this stuff.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="c2579449-be3f-41f5-8c75-e228182cb8f2">
      <Text>ANDREJ climbs on top of DUJE and begins to undress him, slowly and carefully.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="67cbe58e-3e7f-41ef-9753-529f14a553e7">
      <Text>DUJE feels the pocket knife in his right trouser pocket with his right hand, takes it out and starts stabbing ANDREJ in the chest and face.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="dddb2d3e-6854-459a-a24f-afcd55e17649">
      <Text>ANDREJ screams in pain. DUJE stabs him 33 times. Blood is gushing out.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="62eabb88-1ae5-43a8-813c-43c69d04ae00">
      <Text>ANDREJ falls from the bed to the floor.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="369dc11e-021b-4922-a8c4-7a066531c981">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="49" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="8bc71d1f-bb27-4d8b-907d-34de93d290c7">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="55" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. ANDREJ'S LIVING ROOM - NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="a844f6c4-c770-4e43-9125-520b7f05501d">
      <Text>As soon as PERE hears the screams, he gets scared, picks up his fanny pack from the table, gets up from the couch and walks quickly to the front door.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="a73366cc-60d4-4aaa-946a-7baad964c69c">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="9bb746d6-7846-489e-a37a-875e6d4fa59e">
      <SceneProperties Length="1" Page="55" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DUJE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="VUJO">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>INT. ROOM - NOĆ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="9a132ab8-4526-4575-ba58-17eb1f297506">
      <Text>DUJE pulls hard with his left hand and breaks a part of the bed, so he manages to free himself, but he still has the handcuffs attached to his left hand.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="0fb5228e-a28e-4aa8-ae16-07d9e1c392fe">
      <Text>VUJO comes into the room, because he hears ANDREJ screaming.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="17a0dcf0-d6f0-4968-bd6d-621df12d94e9">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="995e669d-f6e9-4c37-9084-5c05e887527a">
      <Text>This guy was going to rape me!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="72ccd252-8c20-4630-8038-be8def33672a">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="d11cdafa-27ae-4b64-8af8-dbddb8f2e72c">
      <Text>What the fuck!?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="6907d08c-833e-484c-b31b-4e5b0845dfed">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="f92840f4-7fcb-4000-a5ed-1b75ac009b39">
      <Text>Did you know anything about this?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="5e002ae8-1eab-4f44-a127-3cc431fdb958">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="7c7bc876-9f59-4e38-87a3-809fefdef00e">
      <Text>No.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e8613c40-f281-4066-925f-a38ae37587a9">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="ff85846f-141b-4459-bf4e-486a93db22ca">
      <Text>I'm gonna fuck your mother.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="ff815ecf-5c4f-42e5-bc60-15876fc64bdc">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="1a5c2dc3-f4fd-4a44-b2f0-3c6bacb201be">
      <Text>Why did you disfigure him like this?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="be246647-457f-4bef-8c74-886f4a5488d3">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="f7ac8d12-651c-4002-acc0-8f49e2bd7022">
      <Text>He was going to fuck me! You knew this. You're as retarded as he is.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7b8890a1-4274-4cdf-b8db-5c2206e0c0fb">
      <Text>VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="b655927b-cc29-4b00-9741-17dd862e0439">
      <Text>I didn't know, bro. How would he know?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="864a4be4-ab22-4d27-855d-c703aee6ba93">
      <Text>ANDREJ </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">screams</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">in</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">pain</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7214b1a5-560b-49be-b6e1-1da89d82f838">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="00e7a63f-eb9d-4190-abe7-fe411a87ea8f">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">What</Text>
      <Text> are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">we</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">gonna</Text>
      <Text> do </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">now</Text>
      <Text>? I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">mean</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">look</Text>
      <Text> at </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">him</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="5fbf0f26-8dd9-484f-97aa-a68db5b02c59">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="468dc73e-bf15-4538-b157-a1e4e4ee9594">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">I'm</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">not</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">gonna</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">be</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">only</Text>
      <Text> one </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">going</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">jail</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">You're</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">going</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">kill</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">him</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="7d6b4913-76a8-47f2-b1fa-193a3f4fa9b5">
      <Text>DUJE </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">VUJO</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">look</Text>
      <Text> at </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">each</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">other</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="04301d0f-d553-403c-bfef-54e004bc5710">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="51" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="0933d322-840d-49c4-935b-d4ffbac796e5">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="56" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">INT</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">ANDREJ'S</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">LIVING</Text>
      <Text> ROOM - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="e05deb98-d6b2-427d-b0a8-33d1935640ac">
      <Text>DUJE </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">goes</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">into</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">living</Text>
      <Text> room. He </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">takes</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">shotgun</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">from</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">wall</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">checks</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">see</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">if</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">it's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">loaded</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="bb605229-9674-4cc7-90d3-ffc2913f258e">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="52" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="82c59c1b-0e0b-4089-8c65-217034324d68">
      <SceneProperties Length="7/8" Page="56" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="ANDREJ">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="DUJE">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="VUJO">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">INT</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">ANDREJ'S</Text>
      <Text> R00M - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="116877e3-f977-4ca8-89ca-a817f74d3034">
      <Text>DUJE </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">gives</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">shotgun</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">VUJO</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="2e63a206-c1c0-4e58-9f26-a48726afa54a">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="b7b95c37-b50e-4269-b323-9f4a8694f628">
      <Text>Take </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">it</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="006c7ad2-c06f-46d6-b3f8-2816dff11fd7">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">VUJO</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="7d06a63a-dd6b-4853-be2b-f6e20033968a">
      <Text>I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">can't</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">kill</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">guy</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="d3ed070e-502f-4a0d-bc9a-934dc70522d9">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="e7506c02-7d38-4530-b317-30c8514ab71c">
      <Text>You </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">don't</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">have</Text>
      <Text> to do </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">anything</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">just</Text>
      <Text> put </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">your</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">finger</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">pull</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">when</Text>
      <Text> I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">tell</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you</Text>
      <Text> to.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="ad9aca5b-528b-4d43-a1d7-45784eaf1620">
      <Text>ANDREJ </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">is</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">screaming</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">crying</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="07f60bd6-2562-4d70-9fff-897b7bc33aa6">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="93c23084-f708-447a-99e7-26416b98b241">
      <Text>Don't!! I beg you like God. What worms you are, you will burn in hell. Faggots! You're only denying your nature. Don't, Dujan, please! I will tell you where I keep everything. Please! Take everything in the vase with flowers. Don't shoot Vejo, my friend!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="9ec253b1-f965-4861-88af-56f3cebce762">
      <Text>3 second pause.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="cbfca766-703d-47ad-8783-560d5b81ccee">
      <Text>DUJE looks VUJO in the eyes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="39a2bd4c-0c35-4eb1-97f5-af5ac6c867cc">
      <Text>VUJO looks away and closes his eyes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="3c447cc1-6d00-4386-97aa-1fa27136ed4f">
      <Text>DUJE </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">aims</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">gun</Text>
      <Text> at ANDREJ.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e2227644-17d9-405f-8cc3-27079398fd88">
      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="a12f72ed-ee64-4133-830a-6dd09e04fe1d">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Now</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="1612c994-2b4f-4389-a032-b76035bf5533">
      <Text>ANDREJ</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="130daadc-567a-4a61-a593-4521e05300c9">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Nooooo</Text>
      <Text>!!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="c37bcb73-9ead-4076-90cb-04b1b0116f8d">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">VUJO</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">pulls</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">trigger</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">shoots</Text>
      <Text> ANDREJ </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">straight</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">in</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">forehead</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
