        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>EXT. KIDS PLAYGROUND - SUNNY DAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="4ca68e7b-0462-4d1e-b7f8-bd7afe4ddf12">
      <Text>MANIRA and PALMINA are swinging in a basket.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="2353cfd6-6580-415a-be7d-666bdbd9f12f">
      <Text>They are kissing.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="6c1234be-a0dd-46ca-baee-a1d8c9090d6f">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="56" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="67fedece-8727-42e0-a5a3-8f7f39008398">
      <SceneProperties Length="3/8" Page="57" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text>EXT. MEADOW - DAY</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="4911df68-3d70-438c-99d1-7cd280e44c34">
      <Text>PALMINA and MANIRA are walking.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="fbb2de2a-8637-429c-919b-5e87952ff42c">
      <Text>PALMINA picks a dandelion. They blow it together and make a wish.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="abc811c1-84c6-4a1d-ab5e-9bc7d762ef7e">
      <Text>PALMINA throws the dandelion on the floor.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="a11d9769-ded7-4f73-8bcc-92de9a733070">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="940fdcdb-faba-4624-a1cf-ce899e46b6d5">
      <Text>The dandelion is lying on the floor, MANIRA steps on it.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="508f4e63-b366-4a48-864c-0ea5afcdcb82">
      <Text>PALMINA and MANIRA continue walking behind the camera.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="5c3b2118-bc3b-4b25-90af-0211a73c45d6">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
