      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">EXT</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">WALKING</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">PATH</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="cc167dd9-bd55-4bd5-80a9-be112304ac41">
      <Text>PALMINA and MANIRA are walking.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a7eb556a-c085-47e8-abf9-948c4e04aa51">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="ce19fb49-9f34-4a94-aea2-4d8e87252087">
      <Text>Would you ever kill?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="eee29286-f66a-47de-a836-bb5f33cac2ce">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="ee81bb97-37c3-4a4b-af82-1fdb6f58b485">
      <Text>I don't know. Maybe I would.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="6ba8dca7-94bf-4e00-be67-4842b3a4090d">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="d44d4701-67c5-4288-8f13-17450edf859f">
      <Text>But then you're going to prison. Why would you do that to yourself?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="fb494ed9-772c-4d3e-a7fe-6a2b92e1c1b5">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="fd4a700d-443a-4fab-bb15-aac87276bc0b">
      <Text>I wouldn't do that to myself, the state would do that to me. And those government officials. Mrš.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="c8d5752e-c06b-4b60-a99e-482291648144">
      <Text>A short pause.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a0a01a7c-67ed-43f9-856a-30332162989f">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="bd7203b4-a11b-419c-952e-1003e2a877d4">
      <Text>A police officer raped a friend of mine.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="9c3cf253-0199-488d-9bc7-073253dac064">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="7d73df10-847c-44b4-8fc7-f842b0544226">
      <Text>What the fuck?! Why didn't she report him?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="12df60ee-0579-492f-bb09-a0fc3930e68f">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="a67f1324-9dd1-409f-b137-c2c41bc46ff3">
      <Text>He's a police officer. They won't do anything to him. He said that himself.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="91effcfa-3452-4b18-9904-98e83374aff4">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="7db4cc3f-a466-493e-b89a-a039ad21e9db">
      <Text>Do you know where he lives?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7825ead5-71bf-4802-94cb-a8a13519d63d">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="bb2f0e0b-99d0-4d7c-95d3-d89780de7ac1">
      <Text>She knows.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="b824e94f-3937-4f5b-9c23-a4c725807756">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="0bcefdb1-3518-4f6c-a29d-ca4dea7a2673">
      <Text>Today, forensics are good, DNA analysis and all that.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e724f502-99bb-4433-8090-f78300987a55">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="30274aff-2a0a-4b3e-ac97-34cc1ccc83d1">
      <Text>I can only imagine how strong the forensics office in Split is. The best thing is to poison him.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="75736437-6634-4b92-8099-78a83f24901c">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="a4335778-f93c-481f-9ddd-308e6087f841">
      <Text>Oleander seeds are poisonous.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="614f6078-232c-446b-8774-c9c47d2c2803">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="11f765b7-e16c-4674-be6d-f1bd21acfb82">
      <Text>But how many do you have to eat for it to be deadly?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="ba616578-7be9-41bf-a7bb-fcf2b3bdc270">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="1a39bad3-c220-4471-86cb-cc95ea1c732f">
      <Text>Probably a lot.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="8402f0d3-e7ce-409a-909a-0c10aac62b39">
      <Text>Short pause.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="73e326be-90e4-4a95-a068-b352ed64bdf7">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="56e69bec-f16c-4f11-955c-94ec481702ad">
      <Text>I would tear him apart with my bare hands.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e8118f20-049f-45de-b7d1-604afc83e713">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="4f528ad2-d947-466b-aa0a-0d64ff45eaa1">
      <Text>What would you do? He's stronger than you.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="19781ccd-d118-4ef1-b981-f6307578ffec">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="9db1875c-3f44-403b-ba70-a572b4135cc4">
      <Text>No. He's weak, that's why he does it.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="b26d6d69-fafd-457f-a4a5-6c3332e0db3d">
      <Text>CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="ab67e5f5-6a45-4ab8-9e83-3aa8222734b2">
      <Text>PALMINA and MANIRA are walking downhill to the Kraljev Gaj beach.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="92df1340-155b-448b-a44e-5b4b160dc8bf">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="0d99125e-910f-48d7-9123-e766c54e9731">
      <Text>Pff.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="b66be7ef-b777-4179-8f96-ce2a6371befc">
      <Text>PALMINA stops.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="f3b473f2-0269-4d6a-a21f-e9559f17428c">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="ad382f0b-2c99-49fa-85b2-cdf1c4b17583">
      <Text>Did you see that?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a3a2c6aa-d08e-44a9-84b4-3959afb134da">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="032cf782-20ea-4bfc-8871-4e57b4441100">
      <Text>What?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="61740a50-77a7-496b-b6af-7920f0dfe940">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="870f8a0e-d5bf-4423-93da-8212bc597b66">
      <Text>A grandma.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="11ef671e-030b-402c-bd6c-481971910b2a">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="8bc78833-af56-453c-bc21-3a80a9dd8dc3">
      <Text>Where?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="0525f7af-1238-4624-b179-9dd7a9c5b404">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="613ce4b7-90e5-4362-afd4-9c04fda44a65">
      <Text>She has black eyes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="0fff5653-8c09-4b71-8aec-e09ebcb3b8fb">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="4f4ee6fd-7c1f-41a4-b1e6-b9dad0dd2e31">
      <Text>That's a tree. Come on, my psychotic girl.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="12f85bdd-16aa-42cc-9d64-e582657a2545">
      <Text>MANIRA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">continues</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">walking</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="0ce2ab86-965b-4ee5-a9c9-51b8c27ffaee">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="64" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="6c131e38-9d93-42b4-8d4b-2a3b5eb1d208">
      <SceneProperties Length="4/8" Page="63" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MANIRA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PALMINA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">EXT</Text>
      <Text>. KRALJEV GAJ BEACH - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="2a9f31e5-6e79-4030-95b1-62b25b25234f">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> MANIRA are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">getting</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">undressed</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7ae2f17e-0f0d-48e3-9948-e0e81bd35302">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="23e4e2f5-5296-4250-901d-58a5f98e5602">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Did</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">it</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">ever</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">happen</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you</Text>
      <Text>?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="c8651a51-1883-402e-b5c7-881281b7ff8d">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="e910a010-b89e-4e64-a0a8-50d93b9331d4">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Once</Text>
      <Text> but I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">don't</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">remember</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">it</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">mostly</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="3dd73ce0-8157-4ad1-a5f2-7e1ea4e56464">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="e9e00d2a-22e5-4183-bc88-aa560d8db6b3">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Would</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">kill</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">him</Text>
      <Text>?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="eec3e639-ea7f-4374-8282-9c22fc70f89e">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="8b649816-34c4-42dd-b0b8-d91414669e92">
      <Text>I </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">kill</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">him</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">everyday</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="cf6f5cb8-fee5-47ac-a985-dc19f818a865">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">jumps</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">in</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sea</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="a26e6706-348c-4e45-b2d5-4a2577989da4">
      <Text>MANIRA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">jumps</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">in</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sea</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="ddb17735-eafe-4041-97c3-639f162b42d0">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="65" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="3c235459-e622-4646-9d4f-7d0a3157baef">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="64" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">INT</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">UNDERWATER</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="f3f6be41-097b-48d9-9b2b-49ec521f993e">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> MANIRA are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">swimming</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">around</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">each</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">other</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">kissing</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="ef7b2324-1e6c-4e05-908f-b0de16dddfa6">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
