      <Text>DUJE</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="81b5222b-4277-4db7-8322-507ddf847607">
      <Text>Pere. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">Where</Text>
      <Text> are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you</Text>
      <Text>?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="3ac0af44-3e80-49d1-8917-dbd4e9524624">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="76" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="0d22a3b5-8b0e-48e0-85f0-03683dce8aaf">
      <SceneProperties Length="1 5/8" Page="74" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MANIRA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PALMINA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">EXT</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">DOCK</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">BAĆINSKA</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">LAKES</Text>
      <Text> - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">SUNSET</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="5f38e4f7-d7bc-4792-8366-a2e08726708a">
      <Text>PALMINA AND MANIRA roll a joint, smoke it, and talk.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="25792ee6-c3d3-4121-b3c8-cc337e032b19">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="002248cd-bef2-4624-9620-e312acecb03d">
      <Text>Unpopular opinion: Serbs make better films.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="1d8e6d01-d8e2-438a-a2c6-77ee55cc9a6d">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="2070eeb4-d9ea-4482-87aa-c5eda2e63a5f">
      <Text>They always make the same film. about crime, war or football. But at least something. And us?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="f51c3b1d-3765-4187-9666-af13e804e937">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="edae2070-016b-4be0-b46a-aa9145a85635">
      <Text>Well, we are in the tourism business.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="8cd0b80f-88db-48a0-9e6b-44ad2c4de914">
      <Text>Pause.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="679e5757-a46e-4572-aee2-3163db014862">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="0a56842d-c227-44ee-9749-49b2e6b478c8">
      <Text>How's psychosis?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="3086677c-6441-4330-96ed-5dee01be941c">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="11b1126f-e47a-490f-af2c-ab170b79d9c8">
      <Text>The best unreal thing I ever saw was that monkey cat.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="5d0c01b9-b4a8-46b0-9649-4ee7d71210b8">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="748ac459-6d6e-4fe5-b550-19b0780dbe8d">
      <Text>Yes, I understand. And why do you think you were seeing that?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="ed1b406b-d203-452b-8e6c-4a63b500da56">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="81025f1d-d98b-4449-9d7b-95fe0f5ed6f5">
      <Text>I don't know. I was sober. It must be stress. Now it switched to the old woman.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="0b6631e8-8d77-4f91-8b90-f794564d3bcd">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="9e46ef9d-0599-4fa7-8e6e-b3201c410d2b">
      <Text>Baba Roga, yes.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="71f78284-3caf-44f5-9138-3bba4aed6228">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="8f7f7d04-b6ba-4202-87b2-5044d0a4225e">
      <Text>She's not bad either.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="aa0fcb7f-090f-46ce-8b02-bb11646ab9ff">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="a94c0d99-45b5-4dc9-baaa-9bebf269f224">
      <Text>Well, she's better than the fat man.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="db52f470-a3a8-4fac-8ede-411c14b46832">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="28f54ba9-3211-47fd-9600-2ce2ec3eda11">
      <Text>Exactly.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="d64b5c73-3cdd-4d20-beef-9fc6f4df6151">
      <Text>Pause.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="851c542d-bc47-4795-9475-e66fbead7799">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="400bffd8-be8a-46a5-a60f-359610c3b292">
      <Text>From zero to ten, how pretty do you think I am?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="9dbd7425-ff4c-438b-801b-594b6809c11c">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="55c23f3d-9145-4427-b985-6b5a5b783ebf">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="36b6b2a2-6db2-414f-85e0-73eaeecbc6a8">
      <Text>9?! What part of me doesn't look good? Mrš.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="19645ee4-a54f-4d18-96ab-40bacaabd2f1">
      <Text>MANIRA (SARCASTICALLY)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="22003b6c-b63d-4372-957b-6f378c7cf3d0">
      <Text>I'm so awful.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="09c9afee-8fda-439c-ad9e-267158dee56b">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="78bdf2a1-9521-4a6f-bdc4-e3706ab888a8">
      <Text>What an evil cunt!</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="19e2c269-3e78-475e-9711-73acd8e87ed8">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="3ef36d82-96e4-4868-b7c9-3794b48df405">
      <Text>Hush, village girl.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="717ef1f4-029f-4cbb-ab8b-d92e6da0669d">
      <Text>MANIRA turns around and looks behind her.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="b076e6d4-2694-4970-b5ec-b4d7d258d9b8">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="e9a42d17-926a-46d4-a4fb-4c0957d910aa">
      <Text>You are the teacher of demons.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="eca8045b-3dd1-49de-80be-3348956a02c4">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="2c022a88-6a54-4849-8a86-90280060d7cb">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">And</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you're</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">jumping</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">out</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">of</Text>
      <Text> a cake for 50 </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">euros</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="6e76ee9d-f950-4f06-9fc8-b94323f68f9a">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="4daa3b5b-c87f-4975-bcf4-9aff95d50f95">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">That</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">was</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">once</Text>
      <Text>. Oh, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">it</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">doesn't</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">bother</Text>
      <Text> me.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="299eef94-18e7-40df-a00a-caa9c867be71">
      <Text>Pause.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="d7032e7a-986a-4d2b-b96b-a53d4a67d128">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="6d0b0108-1aaa-4540-bbb7-7616e02c08de">
      <Text>I am a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">proud</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">bitch</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">cunt</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="11308fe7-2b94-4e61-8de9-30fbe6b79996">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="77" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="54be2a1c-aef9-45d3-b282-8ab94dc32fc3">
      <SceneProperties Length="2/8" Page="75" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats/>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">EXT</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">AMUSEMENT</Text>
      <Text> PARK - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="70905d24-d15e-4c11-b2a9-23ef5bce414c">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> MANIRA are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">high</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sitting</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">in</Text>
      <Text> a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">boat</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">that</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">is</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">rocking</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">left</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">right</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">in</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">an</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">amusement</Text>
      <Text> park.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="83dad5d8-c20b-4b36-a61c-9e85cd7a35c1">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">CUT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" Number="78" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="24" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Scene Heading" id="4611f67f-de62-4e72-9016-6a2d1e35cc81">
      <SceneProperties Length="2 3/8" Page="75" Title="">
        <SceneArcBeats>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MANIRA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="MANNERS">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PALMINA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
          <CharacterArcBeat Name="PALMINA AND MANIRA">
            <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="0.00" OutlineLevel="0" RightIndent="1.39" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No"/>
          </CharacterArcBeat>
        </SceneArcBeats>
      </SceneProperties>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">INT</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">KITCHEN</Text>
      <Text> TABLE - </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">NIGHT</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="6630123c-7aae-4031-86ea-ef7ac7174e37">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> MANIRA are </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">sitting</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">opposite</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">each</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">other</Text>
      <Text> at a table. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">There</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">is</Text>
      <Text> a plate </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">with</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">olives</Text>
      <Text> on </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> table.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="9cec72a8-41c8-4b6e-85e8-870d9efc10b5">
      <Text>In </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">middle</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">of</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">frame</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">there</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">is</Text>
      <Text> a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">candle</Text>
      <Text>, PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">has</Text>
      <Text> lit </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">it</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">with</Text>
      <Text> a </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">lighter</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="559cf44a-6fb7-4cd4-83a1-543582c580f0">
      <Text>MANIRA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">is</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">rolling</Text>
      <Text> a joint.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="8fd9533c-af92-40fb-b898-63eca417013c">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">eats</Text>
      <Text> one </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">olive</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a054c7f8-cc94-4aad-8080-49cbfe643e1a">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="87a78e4b-25ed-44d8-94c7-35ad159e836f">
      <Text>Mauro. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">When</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">we</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">called</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">him</Text>
      <Text> at 4 </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">in</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">morning</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">bring</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">us</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">weed</Text>
      <Text> to </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> park.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7ec9df67-9372-44a8-b25c-e7f13db28cef">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="e5cc3ddb-8edd-46c9-bbd2-7333c81b2859">
      <Text>And he showed up.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="4010b18d-67a4-4ef8-96c5-a8b019cf4d54">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="5268b600-647c-43d6-8aee-08d8b2288e7b">
      <Text>And we hid in that little house at the playground.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="09c840fe-d405-4c23-92b8-e6c8fbf89dec">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="a3a965c8-e74f-49b6-b62c-ed06864bf22b">
      <Text>So he went around in circles for half an hour, and couldn't find us.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="f5fbe2b1-efb6-4964-9524-d605cdcf2f5a">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="9d9f7f68-0b46-426f-89d4-683b319a342c">
      <Text>We peed in the sand.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7b246d7d-24ba-4d1b-b024-4676481c4012">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="3d143f48-dd47-4cbc-85c7-c545a628c420">
      <Text>Like pussy cats.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="3a545b40-3eac-427e-b3de-d8bacd73a111">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="d125d7d2-399f-4f22-8260-816ab6d4e5ad">
      <Text>Then he found us. "Palmina, why are you doing this to me?"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="896c7399-9600-403a-9de6-a67de9bb6361">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="1ebc8216-c020-4d3b-8b19-e6f28e929ccd">
      <Text>"You're so rude"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="1c267d56-6fa5-4a84-948d-6ec41702bf94">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="4fbf3458-7c43-4192-ba11-21aa56caad14">
      <Text>"Pathethic"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="d0debd90-e7a2-4065-b212-dd28ffc5d72d">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="c9b8dced-fbbb-4e7a-8f48-bcbab4d25a24">
      <Text>"Annoying"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="467a63ca-7225-4e38-a265-c2f5cd5e3522">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="ef9c037d-3633-4d4c-b1e6-1d4d0fc15059">
      <Text>"Witch"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="e4750419-2b22-4acd-a7e2-1b84b55f1402">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="52e0ccc2-bb22-4cc6-bf30-5e73fad8e7be">
      <Text>"Crazy bitch"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="dbbd4d19-64d1-410e-b551-402bbf483479">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="0e222949-023e-4fb3-9441-0ea290c3834b">
      <Text>"I love you, and you treat me like this"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="5ccc18b2-221f-4c1a-a7ee-5af813a68581">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="1091f5c3-9b06-4fc1-8fa4-0052175c9838">
      <Text>"You love me, and you treat me like this?"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="081acf74-c359-4f2a-8624-c60de6358a45">
      <Text>Pause.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="887183cc-514b-4893-a693-5909384c35c2">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="c95f22c2-7525-4631-8760-4345e0572f9e">
      <Text>When he was trying to roll a joint, wind blew and everything flew away.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="dcb84d4a-0c61-4343-b38e-2c96ac7491e4">
      <Text>Both laugh.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="3727746c-1bc6-4fb6-89ee-d84f3b9a95d2">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="8bb96d45-8e74-4323-9a39-07775204988a">
      <Text>Then he got on his knees and started picking it off the ground.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="25b079cb-b8b4-4ffd-b1bb-76dc7d65ed95">
      <Text>Both laugh.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="2632c9d4-029d-46ec-b6bf-551d1b3491ae">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="77ef5700-f381-4ad4-8df9-af0f855ae87f">
      <Text>"Turn on the flash!"</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="fca2ac35-cb38-433d-a547-7c4fe0062a88">
      <Text>Both laugh.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="f5e129e3-3f23-46fe-846a-f22a2843f3c4">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="c6924d95-0fd2-4bb6-957a-89b439a713a4">
      <Text>"You shouldn't hang out with Manira. My advice."</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="beab4cbe-1fd6-457d-828f-033a6a043617">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="aedb9975-44cc-4c97-84ca-1a4bf354c38f">
      <Text>You're a bad influence. I was a low maintenance child.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="7f58877b-b135-4fa2-8f8d-7a93daf9c591">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="416584e2-6b42-4fcd-ace2-6a7c74338757">
      <Text>And what now? Relationship problems?</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="a5e6d93f-ccec-4dc7-886a-00c6b4ebcd81">
      <Text>PALMINA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="12caa9cd-6039-48bb-b194-b098cefa104e">
      <Text>I don't have relationships.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="2291da40-6ff7-491a-b804-a76bf4377698">
      <Text>MANNERS</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="d4110c14-94ea-4b7d-aa55-7859301638f9">
      <Text>Well, that.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="a147ef73-e639-4df1-a72c-64bd34aca6a7">
      <Text>Pause.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="5e7a2396-255b-4672-8940-8359f40cd473">
      <Text>MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="5bd3ab94-39f8-4671-aa2e-a2027ae9c356">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">When</Text>
      <Text> he </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">started</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">playing</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">his</Text>
      <Text> music. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">That</Text>
      <Text> song he </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">wrote</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">about</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">you</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.50" RightIndent="7.01" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Character" id="9275fa1c-e7cd-45ce-aa6c-417053f1e640">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">AND</Text>
      <Text> MANIRA</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="-0.10" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="3.00" RightIndent="5.26" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Parenthetical" id="9ebbff4c-690f-4d4a-aefc-019961301db4">
      <Text>(</Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">singing</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> song)</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="2.50" RightIndent="5.76" SpaceBefore="0" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Dialogue" id="7c31ff78-fb07-4aed-b9ad-34d9badb4de8">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">They</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">both</Text>
      <Text> hum </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">the</Text>
      <Text> song for 5 </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">seconds</Text>
      <Text>. </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">They</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">look</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">into</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">each</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">other's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">eyes</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="c9670498-38ab-4f33-b77c-6a4d06e9e3b8">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> MANIRA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">look</Text>
      <Text> at </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">each</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">other</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> smile.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="f6afe484-b113-40f3-aea7-e5bf55d56b64">
      <Text>PALMINA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">and</Text>
      <Text> MANIRA </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">look</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">into</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">each</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">other's</Text>
      <Text> </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">eyes</Text>
      <Text> for 20 </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">seconds</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">silence</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Left" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="1.50" RightIndent="7.26" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Action" id="b86ec315-668f-47bc-abd6-78b56cbb3556">
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">They</Text>
      <Text> start </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">kissing</Text>
      <Text>, </Text>
      <Text AdornmentStyle="-1">slowly</Text>
      <Text>.</Text>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph Alignment="Right" FirstIndent="0.00" Leading="Regular" LeftIndent="5.50" RightIndent="6.86" SpaceBefore="12" Spacing="1" StartsNewPage="No" Type="Transition" id="b39f220d-1ef5-40ec-8af4-85fe0c28a178">
